tags: here's a toast to my real friends
summary: Suzy!!!! Thank you so much for that present!!! You actually took the time to decorate it yourself and I think that is so cute...
body:
Suzy!!!! Thank you so much for that present!!! You actually took the time to decorate it yourself and I think that is so cute and so thoughtful! “Here’s a toast to my real friends” you have no idea how it makes me happy the fact that those lyrics remind you of me! 🙈 And it describes perfectly our relationship! You’ve always been there for me since our paths crossed (thanks to Taylor) and I’ll never be able to thank you enough for everything you’ve done for me! That present, I’ll keep it with me forever! When I have my own house, it will hang on one of my walls and if I have children someday when they point to it, I’ll tell them your name!

Thank you so much for everything @smileonmyfacethekettleon I love you so much! 🥂☺😍😘💜
